{"tid":2107050,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[NHK紀錄片] 你已不在那裡～京都動畫放火事件","createTime":"2020-07-13T15:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T14:36:14.000Z","uid":4618,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7f86982633fe60557a2aa75eaffcc8927cf4c56f","tid":2107050,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T15:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XuTZOgG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXuTZOgG.png&h=4a2d399d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年的7月18日發生了震驚眾人的&ldquo;京阿尼縱火案&rdquo;，日本NHK電視台綜合台官方宣布將於今天（7月13日）播出京阿尼縱火案相關的紀錄片《你已不在那裡～京都動畫放火事件》。<br />\n<br />\n  京都動畫第一工作室在2019年7月18日發生了人為縱火案，這次事件有36人犧牲。事件中的死難者的遺體多數受到嚴重損傷，警方雖規勸親屬們不要去面對遺體，但有的人選擇去見女兒/兒子的最後一面，也有的人決定不去面對面目全非的親人&hellip;。紀錄片將記錄縱火案發生之後這近一年的時間裡，死者家屬們不為人知的苦痛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nhk.jp/p/ts/P2WVR66NRZ/episode/te/Z5M69Q59WX/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhk.jp%2Fp%2Fts%2FP2WVR66NRZ%2Fepisode%2Fte%2FZ5M69Q59WX%2F&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCnwmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=8b6cbd6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nhk.jp/p/ts/P2WVR66NRZ/episode/te/Z5M69Q59WX/</a>"},{"pid":"17393c1e1948b705a11d84b372185cb21b8a821f","tid":2107050,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T15:24:41.000Z","msg":"訪問咗津田幸恵同武本康弘屋企人，睇cap圖都已經好催淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eca7198feacaa01bb360dd6ab4f96d455896eae","tid":2107050,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T15:25:23.000Z","msg":"想哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb57faeed6d13cd062a2cfc5ce739b91668e32e7","tid":2107050,"uid":49057,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T15:26:54.000Z","msg":"武本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3140fd87fa7e7bccdffc3cc07284ddd0e063f960","tid":2107050,"uid":94167,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1